## Safety Features

### Automatic Backup

Fix creates automatic backup before changes:
```
💾 Backup created: <component>-fix-backup-2025-11-13-094800/
```

### Validation Before Completion

Won't complete if:
- ❌ Component tests fail
- ❌ Build fails
- ❌ Full test suite fails
- ❌ Examples don't validate
- ❌ Inconsistencies detected

### Rollback on Failure

If fix fails partway:
```bash
# Restore from backup
cp -r <component>-fix-backup-2025-11-13-094800/* .

# Or use git
git restore .
```

